{"arkId":"cl010111280","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111280","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Mod\u00e8le de paravent","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Mod\u00e8le de paravent"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Restauration (1814-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1817 - 1819","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 558 - Chambre du Roi","room":"Salle 558, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1817,"endYear":1819,"imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Fragonard, Alexandre-\u00c9variste","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1850","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1780","place":"Grasse","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Peintre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q704938"},{"label":"La Hamayde de Saint-Ange, Jacques-Louis de","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1780","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1860","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Dessinateur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q15609782"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11939","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mobilier ; paravent","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Mod\u00e8le de la face du paravent destin\u00e9 \u00e0 \u00eatre tiss\u00e9 \u00e0 la Manufacture des Gobelins pour le Salon de la Paix au Tuileries. Quatre feuilles peintes sur toile et mont\u00e9es dans des cadres de bois.\r\nDans un hexagone bleu, bord\u00e9 d\u0027une frise argent\u00e9e de laurier, se tient un enfant debout entre deux corbeilles de fleurs. Les attributs permettent d\u0027identifier, de gauche \u00e0 droite, l\u0027Architecture, la Po\u00e9sie lyrique, l\u0027Astronomie et la Sculpture. Autour de cet hexagone se d\u00e9veloppe un d\u00e9cor de culots, de rinceaux et d\u0027enroulements, en ton de bronze verd\u00e2tre sur fond brun violac\u00e9. Un tore de feuilles, ponctu\u00e9 de rosaces aux angles, encadre le tout.\r\n\r\nLes dessins d\u0027un meuble en tapisserie pour le salon de la Paix sont command\u00e9s en 1816 au dessinateur Louis de La Hamayde de Saint-Ange. Le paravent se composait de six feuilles. Les cartons sont ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s par Eug\u00e8ne Laurent pour les figures, et Alexandre-Evariste Fragonard pour les ornements. Le meuble est tiss\u00e9 entre 1817 et 1819.\r\nD\u0027autres cartons sont conserv\u00e9s au Mobilier national : une feuille de la face (la Musique ?), et quatre revers.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,44","displayDimension":"1,44 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,17","displayDimension":"1,17 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,65","displayDimension":"0,65 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"53","displayDimension":"53 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : toile (huile sur toile)\r\nTechnique :  (menuiserie)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Gaspard Lavocat (1791-1860), administrateur des Gobelins ; don de sa descendante, 